data.title: University of Minnesota Law School
data.meta_description: First year courses are mostly mandatory courses. In the second and third years, students can choose from a wide variety of course offerings or choose to focus in one of the 11 concentration areas. Extensive experiential learning opportunities are available to build practical skills. Find current class schedules at Academic Planning.
